        <Parent_String>trimming (cutting) [300053074], cutting (shaping or dividing) [300053069], subtractive processes and techniques [300229471], processes and techniques by specific type [300053003], Processes and Techniques (hierarchy name) [300053001], Activities Facet [300264090]</Parent_String>
